      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ASTON JIMENA (6) box seated before sticking on well to finish 0.8 lengths away in third (17.92) at this track in a Other over 305m. Speedy beginner who can find the front despite the tricky draw. Well placed and gets her chance. CANTARA PEARL (2) stalked the lead after a clean break from the tricky draw then burst clear to score (17.86) at this track in a Other over 305m. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and four minor placings to her credit. Should be in this for a long way. FLASH GORDON (4) doesn't win out of turn. Finished second (17.90) at this track latest and might be close to finding winning form again. Has a good record here at this journey. Expected to feature. KAHU (1) was out of the money at this circuit last start but can bounce back.",
